{"id":190773,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/10/维权网-紧急消息：北海律师团在法院门口被围攻/","date":"2011-10-22T17:00:49Z","modified":"2013-02-06T10:25:52Z","title":"维权网 | 紧急消息：北海律师团在法院门口被围攻（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-YB6YlE22WEw/TqF3D9afYLI/AAAAAAAACCA/XSpsrP5BZZ8/s1600/71113-3%25EF%25BC%258C%25E5%25BE%258B%25E5%25B8%2588%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%2589%2593%25E5%2590%258E%25EF%25BC%258C%25E5%259B%25B4%25E6%2594%25BB%25E8%2580%2585%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E9%259A%2594%25E7%25A6%25BB%25E5%259C%25A8%25E6%25B3%2595%25E9%2599%25A2%25E9%2597%25A8%25E5%25A4%2596.jpg\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" name=\"more\">  </a><img border=\"0\" height=\"212\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-YB6YlE22WEw/TqF3D9afYLI/AAAAAAAACCA/XSpsrP5BZZ8/s320/71113-3%25EF%25BC%258C%25E5%25BE%258B%25E5%25B8%2588%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%2589%2593%25E5%2590%258E%25EF%25BC%258C%25E5%259B%25B4%25E6%2594%25BB%25E8%2580%2585%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E9%259A%2594%25E7%25A6%25BB%25E5%259C%25A8%25E6%25B3%2595%25E9%2599%25A2%25E9%2597%25A8%25E5%25A4%2596.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>律师被打后，围攻者被隔离在法院门外</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p></p>\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-RHaUrE4kJDg/TqF3EnoDDoI/AAAAAAAACCI/YC9G2NXM1jo/s1600/71113-1%25EF%25BC%258C%25E8%2583%25B8%25E5%2589%258D%25E6%258C%2582%25E6%2597%2581%25E5%2590%25AC%25E8%25AF%2581%25E7%259A%2584%25E6%2598%25AF%25E5%259B%25B4%25E6%2594%25BB%25E8%2580%2585.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-RHaUrE4kJDg/TqF3EnoDDoI/AAAAAAAACCI/YC9G2NXM1jo/s320/71113-1%25EF%25BC%258C%25E8%2583%25B8%25E5%2589%258D%25E6%258C%2582%25E6%2597%2581%25E5%2590%25AC%25E8%25AF%2581%25E7%259A%2584%25E6%2598%25AF%25E5%259B%25B4%25E6%2594%25BB%25E8%2580%2585.jpg\" width=\"210\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>胸前挂旁听证的是围攻者</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<div><b><span>（维权网信息员金正方报道）</span></b><span>今天（<span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span>月<span lang=\"EN-US\">21</span>日）下午<span lang=\"EN-US\">17</span>：<span lang=\"EN-US\">30</span>分，“裴日红案”庭审休庭后，正要离去的律师团律师在北海市中级法院门口的警戒区内，遭到“裴日红案”被害人黄焕海家属的围攻。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>据现场的律师团成员介绍，有二三十人突然接近律师团成员，这些人当中有很多是今天庭审的旁听者，不少人胸前还挂着旁听证。其中一位妇女扇了徐天明律师一记耳光，将其眼镜打落在地，包括被害人黄焕海父亲在内的十多人冲上来，欲殴打杨金柱律师，幸好杨闪躲及时，不然后果不堪设想。而此时，现场有数十名警察，但未能有效制止。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>据介绍，律师被打后迅速退回法院大厅，要求面见法院院长及相关领导，但一直未获回应。与此同时，围攻律师的数十人仍在法院门外叫骂，而警察并没有对他们采取强制措施。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>截止晚上<span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span>点<span lang=\"EN-US\">30</span>分发稿时，律师团的十多名律师仍在法院大厅内，目前仍在交涉中。据悉，自今年六月介入北海系列案件以来，律师团律师被围攻的事件已发生过多起。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>杨金柱律师：<span lang=\"EN-US\">13908460728</span></span></div>\n<div><span>陈光武律师：<span lang=\"EN-US\">13953912878</span></span></div>\n<div><span>朱明勇律师：<span lang=\"EN-US\">15010580666</span></span></div>\n<div><span>杨学林律师：<span lang=\"EN-US\">13901241513</span></span></div>\n<div><span>周<span lang=\"EN-US\"> </span>泽律师：<span lang=\"EN-US\">13901297271</span></span></div>\n<div><span>李金星律师：<span lang=\"EN-US\">13953129678  </span></span></div>\n<div><span>徐天明律师：<span lang=\"EN-US\">13923456231</span></span></div>\n<div><span>王<span lang=\"EN-US\"> </span>兴律师：<span lang=\"EN-US\">13691192655</span></span></div>\n<div><span>覃永沛律师：<span lang=\"EN-US\">13036818838</span></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>更多北海系列案件的详情，请浏览本网此前的报道：<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://wqw2010.blogspot.com/2011/10/1014.html\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">广西律师案1</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">：“裴日红案”10</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">月14</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">日开庭</span></span></a></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://wqw2010.blogspot.com/2011/10/1014.html\">http://wqw2010.blogspot.com/2011/10/1014.html</a></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>广西律师案<span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span>：一份重要证据或可破局<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://wqw2010.blogspot.com/2011/10/blog-post_5304.html\">http://wqw2010.blogspot.com/2011/10/blog-post_5304.html</a></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>广西律师案<span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span>：北海系列案件介绍<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://wqw2010.blogspot.com/2011/10/blog-post_3637.html\">http://wqw2010.blogspot.com/2011/10/blog-post_3637.html</a></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>广西律师案<span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span>：“裴日红案”的四份起诉书<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://wqw2010.blogspot.com/2011/10/blog-post_9391.html\">http://wqw2010.blogspot.com/2011/10/blog-post_9391.html</a></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>广西律师案<span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span>：警察伪证罪初露端倪<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://wqw2010.blogspot.com/2011/10/blog-post_15.html\">http://wqw2010.blogspot.com/2011/10/blog-post_15.html</a></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>广西律师案<span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span>：裴日红当庭指控警察刑讯逼供<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://wqw2010.blogspot.com/2011/10/blog-post_5799.html\">http://wqw2010.blogspot.com/2011/10/blog-post_5799.html</a></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>广西律师案<span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span>：警察证人当庭威胁律师<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://wqw2010.blogspot.com/2011/10/blog-post_5146.html\">http://wqw2010.blogspot.com/2011/10/blog-post_5146.html</a></span></div>\n<div></d